WEBVTT

00:02:29.880 --> 00:02:32.480
the most important thing to Paul

00:02:33.560 --> 00:02:35.240
was to hold our baby daughter.

00:02:37.240 --> 00:02:39.056
Nine hours later,

00:02:39.080 --> 00:02:40.280
Paul died.

00:02:43.960 --> 00:02:46.216
I've always thought of myself
as a caregiver --

00:02:46.240 --> 00:02:48.296
most physicians do --

00:02:48.320 --> 00:02:51.120
and taking care of Paul
deepened what that meant.

00:02:52.120 --> 00:02:55.736
Watching him reshape
his identity during his illness,

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:59.256
learning to witness and accept his pain,

00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:01.816
talking together through his choices --